2.  For the purpose of paragraph 1 —
"advocate and solicitor", "practising certificate" and "regulated foreign lawyer" have the 
meanings given by section 2(1) of the Legal Profession Act 1966;
"Official Assignee" and "Official Receiver" have the meanings given by section 2(1) of the 
Insolvency, Restructuring and Dissolution Act 2018;
"sub-fund" has the meaning given by section 2(1) of the Variable Capital Companies Act 2018;
"VCC" has the meaning given by section 2(1) of the Variable Capital Companies Act 2018.
